--- !u!114 &8708457752166727022
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1414345796208080801}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5b72b968ab35b7747863b866328637d6, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuizManagerArun
  questions:
  - questionText: '1. In which town did Danila the merchant live? '
    option1: Virginia
    option2: Virata
    option3: Villivakkam
    option4: 'Vardhamana '
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8384fc54f86a38f41a4070396348f249, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 33f50a59820ddd74cbcef4b80e969be0, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
  - questionText: '2. What was the king''s servant name? '
    option1: Govardhana
    option2: Rambo
    option3: 'Goramba '
    option4: Govinda
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c873bc6474b04a34f9826c18d9d9c86a, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 424b49a7370501f438c1161458a527d6, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 5
  - questionText: '3. How did Dantila feel when Gorambha accidentally sat on the
      seat meant for noble people? '
    option1: Honored
    option2: Angered
    option3: Elated
    option4: 'Insulted '
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3f993c8d5de993e4ea5de5c4d80fd7cb, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 3e7dd049e739e5c48b3755cb9fd83174, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 10
  - questionText: '4. When Gorambha was kicked out of the building he... '
    option1: '..bought the building and kicked Dantila out '
    option2: '...complained to the King '
    option3: '...asked Pingalka to eat Dantila. '
    option4: '...swore revenge on Dantila. '
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 676a2299ce9323746a7b7f603a8e5a56, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: b61672d4bef491643b2fe4173eb17224, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 7
  - questionText: '5. Gorambha told the king that he was ..... all night and had
      no sleep at all. '
    option1: 'gambling '
    option2: 'eating ice cream '
    option3: singing
    option4: cooking
    option1IsCorrect: 1
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 6987788810f917b46aaaa0f9ac45a8f5, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: e8bba63914169d14b901b83104dc11e4, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 11
  - questionText: '6. We should never think of anyone as insignificant or too low
      because... '
    option1: 'Mufasa would be upset about it '
    option2: 'that the advice given by Damanaka to all of us. '
    option3: 'he/she may have the power to set us up for failure or sucess alike. '
    option4: 'our opinion about others is insignificant. '
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 1
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: bdde74f4d99d4a643a1f283f061215ec, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: bee1df4bdb0b90044bd9af04754dd610, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 9
  - questionText: '7. Later in the story, Dantila invited Gorambha to his house with
      the intention of... '
    option1: 'talking a revenge on him '
    option2: 'making friends with him  '
    option3: 'playing with him all day. '
    option4: 'making him cook for his family. '
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 1
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 19c71e9fb6e9ee74ea32b66c795015eb, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 67ceb7e4e7c674c40a6e4a3637a76cab, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 9
  - questionText: '8. Simple gestures go a long way in making people... '
    option1: bored
    option2: angry
    option3: jealous
    option4: 'happy '
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c4c352143fc33364db2587cc1b844087, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 7ce65593e82878347803c213535ac7bc, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
  - questionText: '9. When Pingalaka met Sanjaka for the first time.. '
    option1: '...he let out a mighty roar and scared him away. '
    option2: '...he pounched '
    option3: '...he welcomed him and assured his safety. '
    option4: '...he got scared once again and ran away. '
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 1
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 551c30c70b358a54fa066abedbc97c94, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 42850ade8f5dd3c4a80eef562a6c5bcf, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 7
  - questionText: '10. By spending more time with Sanjivaka, Pingalaka became...
      (Select all answers that are correct) '
    option1: '...less interested in royal sports and killing animals. '
    option2: '..more week and made Sanjivaka the king. '
    option3: '...influenced by the bull and his way of life. '
    option4: '...Disillusioned and depressed with the life '
    option1IsCorrect: 1
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 1
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c37eaad28060ed64cbe6a99df35de853, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 5652c4ecbc5c78b40893d94b72a603a7, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 7
  - questionText: '11. The jacakals were distressed because...(Select all answers
      that are correct)   '
    option1: 'Pingalaka banished all jackals from the forest. '
    option2: '...their tails were not fuffly anymore. '
    option3: '...they lost all privileges. '
    option4: "...they didn\u2019t get enough food to eat."
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 1
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c7fbe06fb1a5f8c49b42e543bc1b00c6, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 49aedb32926ba924c9097c524ca05757, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
